5\. Phase 2 - Route Management by Map

  


Requirements

This is an optional phase to include scheduling through a map.

  


Proposal:

  * The default view would only show the next 7 days for scheduling. Pins would be color-coded based on the day of week (Overdue is always red, Monday is always blue, Tuesday is always green, Wednesday is always orange, etc.)
  * The stops on the right would only include items within 25% variance of their scheduled checkin date. (For example, monthly checkins would appear the week before their scheduled date.)
  * Clicking a pin would highlight the matching card on the right.
  * The card on the right would have a similar day of week selector (with an "other" button) that would allow easily rescheduling it to a different day.
